11#ifndef MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_VAD_COMMON_H_
12#define MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_VAD_COMMON_H_
13
14#include <stddef.h>
15
16static const int kSampleRateHz = 16000;
17static const size_t kLength10Ms = kSampleRateHz / 100;
18static const size_t kMaxNumFrames = 4;
19
20struct AudioFeatures {
21 double log_pitch_gain[kMaxNumFrames];
22 double pitch_lag_hz[kMaxNumFrames];
23 double spectral_peak[kMaxNumFrames];
24 double rms[kMaxNumFrames];
25 size_t num_frames;
26 bool silence;
27};

29#endif // MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_VAD_COMMON_H_
